title: Silent Hill 3 playthrough ‚Äî Part 3
description: Loved this game. It's the best one in some ways, although the story is probably the worst. I felt like it really dropped the obscurity of the previous games and made it a little obvious, which makes some sense but I don't know, I like the mystery. Plus it's fun to try and figure it out on your own and come up with your own theories and shit. Good combat though, good environments and enemies. Heather was fun to play as, I think she's a good character. Excited as heck to play the 4th game.
